{"tid":1416364,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"試著說: 佔領機場 正式啟動","createTime":"2019-08-05T14:57:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T08:13:14.000Z","uid":254452,"like":24,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"c65626faef1e212b56f85f6241d8f4d69f06d333","tid":1416364,"uid":254452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T14:57:23.000Z","msg":"原因同好處我唔多講<br />\n隔離都有巴打開左post解釋<br />\n<br />\n[機場防線] 再咁落去我地無可能贏<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1414005\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1414005</a><br />\n<br />\n勇武抗爭係必要的一環，但我地裝備同補給同對家都極不對等，經過呢一段時間，我地手足傷的傷，拉的拉，自身實力不停損耗。<br />\n<br />\n會唔會係時候，大家可以用轁光養晦的方式去長期抗爭！我發夢見到如果將當年的佔領中環變成佔領機場，將會係舒適而有效的方式。<br />\n<br />\n除左可以去機場行下坐下，嫌交通費貴的朋友咪帶埋帳篷去等接機嚕，早左幾日去接朋友，我諗唔犯法掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">佔領機場<br />\n正式啟動</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"b4ff6651d33ccf1fc9fe60053db68d406f6b34fa","tid":1416364,"uid":254452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:00:05.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"5396fa68c60fbadb276f57e36769fd7c4f04f769","tid":1416364,"uid":35815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:03:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8eea0d88636cd9bfe383e8b4f5bdd3d913ae4857","tid":1416364,"uid":154486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:04:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f9b528f4291ed13b5be58b28ce51914f362e441a","tid":1416364,"uid":182575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:06:33.000Z","msg":"已經入緊"},{"pid":"853229beb9a59acc5fa92e1a12dbc0e92311da69","tid":1416364,"uid":290279,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:10:23.000Z","msg":"輿論輸咗返唔到轉頭，佔機場真心諗諗先...please please<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3629ad82e6b8bbc14235a67194d392808275c12","tid":1416364,"uid":2832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime